DEFAULT

./std_bench/global_alignment_protein ./std_bench/data/uniprot_1000.fa std_bench/data/result_pw_global_protein.txt -tc 4

SYNOPSIS

Global Pairwise Alignment benchmark demo (Protein) [OPTIONS] IN OUT

DESCRIPTION

IN is a .fa / fasta input file. OUT is a txt output file.

Settings:

-tc, --threads INT

Number of threads Default: 4.

VERSION
